      <title>阿根廷 11 月通胀在 Milei 贬值前加速</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/argentina-november-inflation-quickened-before-milei-devaluation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 大幅货币贬值之前，阿根廷 11 月份通胀率飙升至 160% 以上，这可能会进一步加速本月物价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/argentina-november-inflation-quickened-before-milei-devaluation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 19:16:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗准备选举，委内瑞拉预算几乎翻倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/venezuela-nearly-doubles-2024-budget-amid-tensions-with-guyana</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗准备总统选举并预计将有额外支出用于保卫埃塞奎博领土，委内瑞拉 2024 年预算几乎翻了一番，达到 7300 亿玻利瓦尔，相当于 205 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/venezuela-nearly-doubles-2024-budget-amid-tensions-with-guyana</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 18:55:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党参议员表示他们正在权衡拜登的移民提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/republican-senators-say-they-re-weighing-biden-immigration-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党参议员周三表示，总统乔·拜登提议改变美国边境政策，这提高了两党就移民和援助乌克兰达成协议的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/republican-senators-say-they-re-weighing-biden-immigration-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 18:33:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非在解决工作签证混乱问题上迈出了重要一步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/south-africa-takes-major-step-toward-fixing-work-visa-mess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，南非内政部长签署了工作许可法规修改计划，旨在解决令该国最大投资者感到沮丧并加剧技能危机的官僚主义困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/south-africa-takes-major-step-toward-fixing-work-visa-mess</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 18:25:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克的盟友认为保守党右翼错过了移民法案的最佳机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/sunak-allies-sense-tory-right-missed-best-shot-at-migration-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)在击退了保守党右翼的叛乱并赢得了对其标志性移民政策的投票后，明显松了一口气。英国首相在议会拥抱了他的首席政治执行者，兴高采烈的助手们喝着威士忌庆祝到周二深夜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/sunak-allies-sense-tory-right-missed-best-shot-at-migration-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 18:21:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Eskom 要求政府入股该公司以减轻债务负担</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/eskom-said-to-seek-equity-swap-for-portion-of-its-bailout-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非负债累累的国家电力公司 Eskom Holdings SOC Ltd. 告诉投资者，它已要求国家财政部将 160 亿兰特（8.4 亿美元）的救助资金转换为股权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/eskom-said-to-seek-equity-swap-for-portion-of-its-bailout-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 17:00:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟为匈牙利提供100亿欧元支持欧尔班</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/eu-unlocks-10-billion-of-funding-for-hungary-in-boost-for-orban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟决定向匈牙利提供超过 100 亿欧元（合 108 亿美元）的援助，这是总理欧尔班·维克多 (Viktor Orban) 在一场关键的乌克兰峰会之前取得的重大胜利，这位民族主义领导人威胁要破坏这次峰会。福林兑欧元涨幅扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/eu-unlocks-10-billion-of-funding-for-hungary-in-boost-for-orban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 16:35:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国议员通过出口、制裁法案瞄准中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/lawmakers-target-china-with-export-controls-sanctions-bills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院一个小组正着手推进四项措施，旨在让美国商务部对中国采取更强硬的态度，其中包括要求提高许可决策透明度的法案，并在哪些技术和企业受到限制方面给予其他机构更多发言权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/lawmakers-target-china-with-export-controls-sanctions-bills</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 16:26:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的纽约欺诈案审判结束。以下是亮点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/trump-civil-fraud-trial-to-resume-in-january-as-primaries-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州针对唐纳德·特朗普的民事欺诈审判在今年剩余时间里一直处于中断状态，法官可能会在一月份第一届总统提名竞赛开始时做出裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/trump-civil-fraud-trial-to-resume-in-january-as-primaries-start</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 13:35:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国为明年再次违反债务规则敞开大门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/german-coalition-won-t-suspend-debt-restrictions-again-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国执政联盟同意明年自 2019 年以来首次恢复对新增借款的限制，同时明确表示该计划可能行不通，从而化解了一场政治危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/german-coalition-won-t-suspend-debt-restrictions-again-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 10:44:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
